description: Proposal under Section 73 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 to vary the terms of the application reference 08/03277FULM for the re-development of the site to allow the ground floor of the Town Hall building to be used as a surgery (Class D1), minor amendments of the upper floors of the Town Hall building to provide one additional 1 bed unit resulting in a total of 15 units comprising 8 units on the first floor (4 X 1 bed and 4 X 2 bed) and 7 on the second floor (4 X 1 bed and 3 X 2 bed) and revised car parking spaces and pedestrian linkages.
